<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Darren Ybarra</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag  "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Picture", class: 'profile-img' %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I am a DevOps Engineer at iHeartMedia. Check out my website! This website uses all the latest and greatest features 
        of Rails including Action Cable, authentication using Devise, authorization using Petergate, AJAX, Javascript, CoffeeScript,
        and many other useful gems to make Rails development easy and simple.</p>

        <p>This content is for learning purposes in order to increase my skills as a Web Developer using Ruby on Rails. 
        This website utilizes Rails best practices that focuses on highly focused communication and transparent design patterns</p>    

        <p>
          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type='button'
            data-toggle='collapse'
            data-target='#jobHistory'
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='jobHistory'
          >
            Job History 
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type='button'
            data-toggle='collapse'
            data-target='#schoolHistory'
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='schoolHistory'
          >
            School History 
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">Job1</div>
            <div class="card card-block">Job2</div>
          </div>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="schoolHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">School 1</div>
            <div class="card card-block">School 2</div>
            <div class="card card-block">School 3</div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>